-- morphism levels before object levels. See note [category_theory universes].
theorem raised_cone_lowers_to_original [is_connected J] {B : C} {F : «expr ⥤ » J (over B)}
    (c : cone («expr ⋙ » F (forget B))) (t : is_limit c) : (forget B).map_cone (raise_cone c) = c := by tidy
